  <h1>Architecture Decision Records</h1>
  <p>
    Architecture Decision Records (ADRs) document significant technical choices made during the design and development of EncodeSwarmr. Each record captures the context, decision, and consequences so that future contributors can understand why the system is built the way it is.
  </p>

